data.description: Beautiful contemporary home in a peaceful wooded setting. With views of Lake Beaverfork in the winter, and a park-like setting year round, this home is an outdoor entertainer's dream. From the large back deck, to trails, to the fire pit, there are many ways to enjoy nature at this property. Inside, you'll find a remodeled home with tons of character. The kitchen is light and airy with tall ceilings and natural light. The living room has a cozy feel with a stunning painted rock fireplace, wood mantle, and gray accent wall that ties the room together. Vaulted ceilings in the primary suite with a private door to the deck that overlooks the forest and Lake Beaverfork. The other bedroom's are large, with 3 bedrooms total upstairs. Updates include new paint in most rooms, new flooring downstairs, new light fixture in dining room, and all new stairs. Downstairs you'll find another living area, bedroom, bath and laundry. The home also features a large shop/hobby area with access from the downstairs. Great location.  Just 10 minutes from downtown Conway, but feels like you are far away from the city.
